# FocusMeet AI Service

Gemini API Key: set GEMINI_API_KEY in your environment
Whisper model: base (change to small/medium/large-v3 for better accuracy)
Whisper device: cpu (change to cuda if GPU available)

# Database
DATABASE_URL=postgresql://focusmeet:focusmeet_secret@localhost:5432/focusmeet

# Redis
REDIS_HOST=localhost
REDIS_PORT=6379
